name: Never ending interiors 001
description:
Neve ending interiors
This is a very special series of 3d collages and sketches I created through first months of heavy quarantine when covid hit while living alone. 
I was discovering changes that happened in me during those lonely times and was exploring themes of loneliness, peace and interiors.

This collection is more subtle, vulnerable and painterly.
At that time I was redescovering painting so the skethes are nice bonus.
